<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Transaction Report</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #4b0082; /* Indigo color */
      font-size: 24px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
      color: #555;
    }

    .highlight {
      color: #4b0082;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #888;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      background-color: #4b0082;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .table {
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: 20px;
      border-collapse: collapse;
    }

    .table th, .table td {
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: left;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }

    .table th {
      background-color: #4b0082;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .table td {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }

    .table .amount {
      text-align: right;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #4b0082;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Transaction Report</h1>
    <p>Dear User,</p>
    <p>We hope you're doing well. Please find below your transaction report, which includes all your <span class="highlight">expenses</span>, <span class="highlight">savings</span>, and <span class="highlight">investments</span> for your records.</p>
    <p><span class="highlight">Report generated on:</span> <%= currentDate %></p>

    <table class="table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Date</th>
          <th>Description</th>
          <th>Amount (Rs.)</th>
          <th>Type</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <% transactions.forEach(function(transaction) { %>
          <tr>
            <td><%= new Date(transaction.createdAt).toLocaleDateString() %></td>
            <td><%= transaction.description || 'No description' %></td>
            <td class="amount">Rs. <%= transaction.amount %></td>
            <td><%= transaction.type %></td>
          </tr>
        <% }) %>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <a href="#" class="btn">View Full Report</a>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>Thank you for using our Expense Tracker Service!</p>
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to contact us.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
